dev.nokee.ide.visualstudio

Interface VisualStudioIdeProjectExtension

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    VisualStudioIdeWorkspaceExtension

    public interface VisualStudioIdeProjectExtension
    The configuration for mapping a Gradle project to Visual Studio projects. The project extension is register to sub-projects where the Visual Studio IDE plugin is applied. The workspace extension, that is VisualStudioIdeWorkspaceExtension, is register to the root project instead.
    Since:
    0.5
